g justice, in his youth Hippò left the breath of life.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>Guarducci: Onorando la saggezza e venerando la giustizia, Hippò in gioventù il soffio lasciò della vita.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 42.0848 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Lavore 1985 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001886\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001886</a>  </li><li> Guarducci 1987 404 no.11 fig.132 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001923\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001923</a>  </li><li> Brugnone 1988-1989 354-355 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002120\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002120</a>  </li><li> Di Stefano 1998 229 fig.27 (cf. SEG 48.1244) <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002033\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002033</a>  </li><li> Di Stefano 2013 27-28 dr <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002031\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002031</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
